<committee-appointment-paragraph><header>Committee on Energy and Commerce:</header><text>Mr. Pallone.</text></committee-appointment-paragraph> <committee-appointment-paragraph><header>Committee on Financial Services:</header><text>Ms. Waters.</text></committee-appointment-paragraph>

